      <title>Aditum 的 Chowdhry 预计 2024 年将降息两到三次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/aditum-s-chowdhry-sees-two-or-three-rate-cuts-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Aditum Investment Management 全球固定收益和多种资产战略主管 Omer Chowdhry 表示，他预计年底前将有 2-3 次降息，主要原因是就业市场疲软。他在 Horizo​​ns Middle East &amp; Africa 上与 Joumanna Bercetche 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/aditum-s-chowdhry-sees-two-or-three-rate-cuts-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:35:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国航空下调利润预期，首席商务官拉贾离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/american-airlines-cuts-profit-outlook-cco-raja-departs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国航空修改了第二季度调整后盈利预期，并宣布首席商务官 Vasu Raja 离职。Sid Philip 在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/american-airlines-cuts-profit-outlook-cco-raja-departs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:34:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BMO 盈利因拨备高于预期而低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/bmo-earnings-miss-estimates-on-higher-than-expected-provisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者和企业难以应对更高的利率，蒙特利尔银行为应对潜在信贷损失拨备了比预期更多的资金，因此该银行的业绩不及分析师预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/bmo-earnings-miss-estimates-on-higher-than-expected-provisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团拒绝必和必拓延长报价期限的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/anglo-rejects-bhp-s-request-to-extend-offer-deadline-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 不会再给必和必拓集团 (BHP Group) 任何时间来承诺收购要约，这标志着两大矿业巨头之间长达五周的争斗达到了高潮，此时距离必和必拓承诺收购要约的最后期限仅剩几个小时。威尔·肯尼迪 (Will Kennedy) 在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/anglo-rejects-bhp-s-request-to-extend-offer-deadline-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:08:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团不会延长必和必拓的最后期限，标志着大型竞购的结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/anglo-won-t-extend-bhp-deadline-threatening-end-to-takeover-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团表示，不会再给必和必拓集团时间来承诺收购要约，这可能会终止这家全球最大矿业公司 490 亿美元的收购计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/anglo-won-t-extend-bhp-deadline-threatening-end-to-takeover-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 09:20:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票结束前几天，印度赢得标普评级展望提升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/s-p-raises-india-s-rating-outlook-to-positive-on-strong-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级表示，未来几个月印度的主权信用评级可能会上调，这将在选举结果公布前不到一周给总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政府带来提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/s-p-raises-india-s-rating-outlook-to-positive-on-strong-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 08:04:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
